# Habit Tracker 2026 - Environment Configuration
# ================================================
#
# This file contains configuration templates for your deployment.
# DO NOT commit real API keys to version control!

# ==========================================
# SUPABASE CONFIGURATION
# ==========================================
# 
# 1. Go to https://supabase.com and create a free project
# 2. Navigate to Settings > API
# 3. Copy these values:

SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project-id.supabase.co
SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your-anon-public-key

# ==========================================
# ADMIN DASHBOARD KEY
# ==========================================
#
# This is a simple access key for the admin dashboard.
# Change this to a strong, unique value before deployment!

ADMIN_KEY=habit2026admin

# ==========================================
# HOW TO SET UP
# ==========================================
#
# STEP 1: Create Supabase Project
# -------------------------------
# 1. Sign up at https://supabase.com
# 2. Create a new project
# 3. Wait for project to initialize
#
# STEP 2: Run Database Schema
# ---------------------------
# 1. Go to SQL Editor in your Supabase project
# 2. Copy contents of supabase-schema.sql
# 3. Run the SQL to create tables and functions
#
# STEP 3: Update Configuration in Code
# ------------------------------------
# 1. Open supabase.js
# 2. Replace 'YOUR_SUPABASE_PROJECT_URL' with your Supabase URL
# 3. Replace 'YOUR_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY' with your anon key
#
# 4. Open admin.html
# 5. Update SUPABASE_CONFIG with same values
# 6. Change ADMIN_KEY to a secure value
#
# STEP 4: Deploy to Netlify
# -------------------------
# 1. Push code to GitHub
# 2. Connect repository to Netlify
# 3. Deploy!
#
# ==========================================
# SECURITY NOTES
# ==========================================
#
# - The anon key is safe to expose in client-side code
# - Row Level Security (RLS) protects the database
# - The admin key is just a simple gate, not high security
# - For production, consider using Supabase Auth for admin access
#
# ==========================================
# PRIVACY COMMITMENT
# ==========================================
#
# This app is designed with privacy in mind:
# - Habits are ONLY stored in localStorage (never sent to server)
# - Only name, first_visit, and last_active are stored in Supabase
# - Analytics are aggregated and anonymous
# - No tracking scripts, no behavior monitoring
